casebody.data:
No. 10-1091. Colorado, Petitioner v. Jeffrey Allen Key. 564 U.S. 1033, 131 S. Ct. 3061,

180 L. Ed. 2d 881,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 4912. June 27, 2011.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals of Colorado. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Colorado granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the Court of Appeals of Colorado for further consideration in light of Davis v. United States, 564 U.S. 229, 131 S. Ct. 2419, 180 L. Ed. 2d 285 (2011).
